HEADWORD: Uptown
<hw>Up*town"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>To or in the upper
part of a town; <as>as, to go <ex>uptown</ex></as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.
U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
