==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Uptown
<hw>Up"town`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Situated in, or
belonging to, the upper part of a town or city; <as>as, a
<ex>uptown</ex> street, shop, etc.; <ex>uptown</ex> society.</as></def>
<mark>[Colloq. U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uptrace</ent>⟦br⟧
